      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلنَّوْمُ رَاحَةٌ لِلْجَسَدِ وَ اَلنُّطْقُ رَاحَةٌ لِلرُّوحِ وَ اَلسُّكُوتُ رَاحَةٌ لِلْعَقْلِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5865 - Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), peace be upon him, said:\n\"Sleep is rest for the body, speech is rest for the soul, and silence is rest for the mind.\""
        ]
      }
